Company Overview of Reservoir Capital Group



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Reservoir Capital Group is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to family office, endowment, and pension fund Limited Partners. It invests in private equity, public equity, fixed income, and alternative markets of the United States. The firm primarily invests in public securities and private investments employing a fundamental analysis with an opportunistic approach. Reservoir Capital Group was founded in 1998 and is located in New York, New York.


